titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: TPRG-SEND TWO YEAR CORRECTED AGE OUTCOME ASSESSMENT SCORE (DEVELOPMENT QUESTION D) - Description

div.p: TPRG-SEND TWO YEAR CORRECTED AGE OUTCOME ASSESSMENT SCORE (DEVELOPMENT QUESTION D) is the PERSON SCORE for question D of the Development section of the TPRG-SEND Two Year Corrected Age Outcome Assessment.
The question asks "Will you be referring the child for a detailed neurodevelopmental assessment?".
